First off...sweet card. I absolutely love it. 

Technically speaking, it has a lot of flaws...back centering, print defects, etc,.  But ask most freak collectors and I'm sure they will tell you that the grade (if it grades at all) doesn't matter. The more crazy, the better :)
How do you guys get the SGC holder to look so clean?  I'd love to learn the trick if anyone wants to share.

If this was an E card I would be in the mix, but T206 freak collectors typically have deeper pockets than me. Good luck on the sale. Awesome card!!
